2024.name: Bio Brawl 2024
2024.description: Bio Brawl is a competition where students will be tested on their knowledge of biology.
2024.rules: 1. Students must be in teams of 2-4. 2. Students must have a device with internet access. 3. Students must have a webcam.
2024.prizes: 1st Place: $100 Amazon Gift Card, 2nd Place: $50 Amazon Gift Card, 3rd Place: $25 Amazon Gift Card
